<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2902291" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">首先，这是聚类分析的问题……<br>题主可以参考这文里的方法：<a href="http://www.guokr.com/article/436974/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">“韩国小姐”的脸到底有多相似？<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><br>将 20 张脸<br><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/41fab96f43c012f479f6c53ba0f0aed0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="486" data-rawheight="503" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="486" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/41fab96f43c012f479f6c53ba0f0aed0_r.jpg">SVD 分解出特征脸<br><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/79308fe9016b4d5bad725adc8524ff28_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="560" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/79308fe9016b4d5bad725adc8524ff28_r.jpg">然后就可以聚类啦~<br><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/943d94b59ed6487e4fb63e2a3cf5c02a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/943d94b59ed6487e4fb63e2a3cf5c02a_r.jpg">
